name: Patient Intake Profile Tool
description:
It is a pleasure to have you here today. Please fill out this pre-visit questionnaire to help us put together your personalized health profile. I review each and every answer personally and use this knowledge to help optimize your treatment. Your answers remain confidential and will not be shared outside of your care circle.

Thank you,

Dr. Shehzad Niazi
